      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IM HAVINTOTROT (7) has been racing well against some good three-year-olds so far this campaign including a fresh win at Bathurst before a Listed placing. Last start led and boxed on for a 2.7m third in the Lunar Lass Trot at Bendigo so he has the early pace to go forward from the wide draw and this suits. WITH APLOMB (6) goes up in grade but has been hard to fault of late, winning her last two starts from back row draws. Owns a good record at this distance so can go well again. RUN FOREST RUN NZ (5) is on the radar after his last-start fourth here week-and-a-half ago and he did put together a string of top-three finishes earlier in the campaign. KYVALLEY MICHAEL NZ (12) broke last start but won the last time he raced away from Melton.",
